//00C487B4
procedure TCoresDocumentacao.SalvarClick(Sender:TObject);
begin
{*
 00C487B4    push        ebp
 00C487B5    mov         ebp,esp
 00C487B7    add         esp,0FFFFFFEC
 00C487BA    push        ebx
 00C487BB    xor         ecx,ecx
 00C487BD    mov         dword ptr [ebp-10],ecx
 00C487C0    mov         dword ptr [ebp-14],ecx
 00C487C3    mov         dword ptr [ebp-0C],edx
 00C487C6    mov         dword ptr [ebp-4],eax
 00C487C9    xor         eax,eax
 00C487CB    push        ebp
 00C487CC    push        0C48932
 00C487D1    push        dword ptr fs:[eax]
 00C487D4    mov         dword ptr fs:[eax],esp
 00C487D7    lea         edx,[ebp-14]
 00C487DA    mov         eax,[00D13338];^Application:TApplication
 00C487DF    mov         eax,dword ptr [eax]
 00C487E1    call        006A22DC
 00C487E6    mov         eax,dword ptr [ebp-14]
